OL,4,Ccrisis, councils warn
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "There are
OL,8,Funacceptable health inequalities
OL,9,Facross the UK and we are determined to
OL,10,Ftackle them to help people live
OL,11,Flonger, happier and healthier lives.
OL,13,F"The NHS is broken. We will get the
OL,14,FNHS back on its feet and shift the
OL,15,Ffocus from simply treating sickness to
OL,16,Fprevention.
OL,18,F"Our 10 Year Plan for Health will
OL,19,Foutline how we will ensure men are
OL,20,Fable to access the support and
OL,21,Ftargeted interventions they need.
