OL,4,Ccrisis, councils warn
OL,6,F"Our plans to reduce obesity, improve
OL,7,Fcancer survival rates and enhance
OL,8,Fmental health services will also help
OL,9,Fto tackle the main drivers of poor
OL,10,Fhealth in men."
OL,12,FThe call by the LGA echoes that of
OL,13,Fcharity group Movember, which
OL,14,Fpublished a report in July warning
OL,15,Fthat more than 133,000 men die early
OL,16,Fevery year in the UK.
